 pepper and lamb mince and mix <b>30 sec\/\/speed 3<b>. Transfer to a bowl, with oiled hands, shape small meatballs (Ø 3 cm) and place them into prepared Varoma dish and tray. Set aside."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Steamed meatballs, spicy tomato rice and sauce"},{"content":"Place simmering basket onto mixing bowl lid, weigh in rice, rinse below running water. Place simmering basket in a bowl with enough water to cover the rice and set aside to soak. Meanwhile go on with the recipe."},{"content":"Place coriander seeds into clean and dry mixing bowl and dry roast <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>, then grind <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside."},{"content":"Place garlic, onions and olive oil into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>."},{"content":"Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and then sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add reserved ground coriander seeds and cook <b>1 min\/100°C\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Add chillies, tomatoes, vegetable stock paste, oregano, salt and pepper and chop <b>30 sec\/speed 6<b>."},{"content":"Insert simmering basket with rice, add water and mix with aid of spatula. Place Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 4<b>. Set Varoma aside, remove simmering basket with aid of spatula, transfer rice into a bowl and moisture the rice by adding 200 g of cooking liquid from the mixing bowl. Mix gently with a fork and set aside."},{"content":"Place closed Varoma back into position and steam <b>7 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Set Varoma aside."},{"content":"Add cornflour into mixing bowl and reduce sauce <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>, without measuring cup. Transfer meatballs to a serving dish, pour remaining sauce on top and garnish with finely chopped fresh coriander. Serve warm with reserved rice."}],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 5m","4 portions"]}